content.rendered:
Directed by Sanjeev Sharma.

Written by Sanjeev Sharma.

Cast Manoj Bajpayee(Pappi Jaatwala). Vijay Raaz(Jaggi Tirchha). Aditi Sharma(Sona). Annu Kapoor(Bichhi). Kay Kay Menon(Tejpal). Aparshakti Khurana(Khappe). Nitin Bhasin(Haggu). Jatin Sarna(Babbe Tashni). Vipul Vig(Ajji Phodu). Anupam Kher(Diwan Saab). Lushin Dubey(Sona’s Mother). Sunita Shirole(Sakina Bi). Brijesh Karanwal(Altoo). Ashok Pathak(Gulaab). Kailash Thakur(Baiju). Kaliprasad Mukherjee(Psychiatrist (as Kali Prasad Mukherjee)). Tanvir Singh(Psychiatrist). Rajat Bhalla(Mahendra). Raman Khanna(Mahendra’s Wife). Rakesh Sharma(Insp. Sherawat). Sada(Dancer on Stage). Ankita Shukla(Singer on Stage). Amit Vasishth(Head Const. Rampal). Pawan Nagpal(Const. Musaddi). Anjor Sharma(Palmist). Saurabh(Tinni). Deepa Bhalla(Savita Bhabhi). Ajitabh Sahai(Manua Paanwala). Sachin(Sabziwala). Amit Bhatia(Lover Boy). Ayushi Mishra(Bindu). Anita Bobal(Mother at Haggu’s Shop). Shrilekha Gaherwar(Daughter at Haggu’s Shop). Ishwar(Lotterywala). Mohammed Irshad(Cobbler). Dinesh Ahlawat(Lala Kishanchand). Saleem Bhai(Barber) . Akbar(Cyclist). Amarjeet(Bichchi’s Victim At Cyclodrome). Ambrish(Mistry 1). Virender Anand(Langda Kabootarbaaz). Arjun(Ardali). Sidharth Bhardwaj(Meter Reader (as Siddhart)). Deepak(Thief 2). Meysam Eddie(Jimmy). Ekta(House Keeper). Anoop Ghosh(Mayapuri Car Dealer). Ginni(Ramesh). Habib(Bijli Bone Setter). Bhushan Ji(Khappe’s Boss). Kazim(ldol Confiscater). Kamal D. Khatak(Security Guard at Mental Hospital). Rajesh Kumar(Mistry 2). Mukesh Manas(Admin Officer). Manprit(Girl In The Green Room). Ashok Mishra(Jama Car Dealer). Neeraj(Warden). Anil Rasal(Gardener). Shahrukh(Thief 1). Anup Kumar Sharma(Office Boy at Mental Hospital). Kawal Soni(Bookie). SÃ¸nu(Dwarf). Jitendra Vasishtha(Clerk). Vicky(Car Salesman)

Language Hindi.

Producers Vishal Bajaj. Shital Bhatia. Faisal Malik. Rohit Nag. Neeraj Pandey. Kumud Shahi. Kawal Soni.

Production Friday Filmworks.
